description: An object representing a previous successful login for a User.

id.description: __Read-only__ The unique ID of this login object.

ip.description: __Read-only__ The remote IP address that requested the login.

restricted.description: __Read-only__ True if the User that attempted the login was a restricted User, false otherwise.

status.description: __Read-only__ Whether the login attempt succeeded or failed.

username.description: __Read-only__ The username of the User that attempted the login.
